{"tid":2393320,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"上次邊個話要睇福建炒飯嫁","createTime":"2021-02-03T11:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T15:34:03.000Z","uid":239860,"like":75,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"62de4ed4d9ffb854dc7e4d845c18603cdd52f26a","tid":2393320,"uid":239860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見，早兩星期個D片太廢，連登仔應該覺得太易，所以就冇係到開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今次就出左福建炒飯，之後有人留言過想睇，其實一早拍好，但未得閒出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以睇下條片<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bzghMznBm3A&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbzghMznBm3A%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=3e1b3d02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bzghMznBm3A&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n製成品<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vouzwgQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvouzwgQ.jpg&h=7bef3e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n材料有雞排、蝦、菇、菜、火鴨、甘荀、瑤柱呢幾樣主要既<br />\n將全部切粒<br />\n瑤柱就之前一早蒸好，所以就係雪櫃攞返出黎蒸熱佢就得(有興趣睇蒸瑤柱既可以去盤菜上集睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPiXt4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPiXt4a.jpg&h=0188d7a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KT7dMQR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKT7dMQR.jpg&h=0bde328c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QkvyMQ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkvyMQ0.jpg&h=c33839f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後將雞同蝦輕輕調一調味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qKh1VKV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqKh1VKV.jpg&h=c4a4d75d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n再炸一炸佢先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MqOMnp5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqOMnp5.jpg&h=69144015&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n之後就開始處理個飯啦，打左隻蛋落去先，  未熟哂既同時就將煲好左既飯倒埋落去炒(如果即場煲飯就唔好落咁多水)，再輕輕調下味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NUFyMR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNUFyMR3.jpg&h=adaa5dd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加入雞湯，再將頭先既雞同蝦、汆左水既菜粒同甘荀粒倒落去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1SEHrh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1SEHrh.jpg&h=b9bf085b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n最後又係調味，再落返生粉水就搞掂了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bydc2ru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbydc2ru.jpg&h=b1ed08dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有興趣就訂閱埋我個ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nig: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CGaAioqJrXL/?igshid=17jre4m7bfvma\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGaAioqJrXL%2F%3Figshid%3D17jre4m7bfvma&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjanpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=90deab75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGaAioqJrXL%2F%3Figshid%3D17jre4m7bfvma&h=f5148637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CGaAioqJrXL/?igshid=17jre4m7bfvma</a>"},{"pid":"aafdfe4541506636f4ff816bf47b374bac4f9fb0","tid":2393320,"uid":35758,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T11:15:05.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪我<br />\n𣎴過勁鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eaf5e794546632c7c70483e510dac7b518c2b71","tid":2393320,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-